Class EphemeralPlaylist

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.tofind.commusica.media.EphemeralPlaylist
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IPlaylist

    public class EphemeralPlaylist
extends Object
implements IPlaylist
    This class represents a playlist that is currently constructed. This is the "Playing" playlist in the UI.
